text: Guo Junjun (; born 2 January 1991 in Dalian, Liaoning) is a Chinese female swimmer. At the 2014 Asian Games in Incheon, South Korea,Dalian Evening Newspaper: （韩国仁川亚运会）女子4×200米自由泳接力中国摘金,大连姑娘郭君君打头阵 (2014-09-24), Chinanews.com: 中国日进六金 (2014-09-23) Guo'group of four people won the Champion in the 4 × 200 m freestyle relay event in time of 7:55.17 in the final, 1:58.09 by herself. she is also the silver goldlist for 4 × 200 m title at 2015 World Championships in Kazan, Russia.Tianjinwe.com: 中国女队4×200米自由泳接力摘银 (2014-12-05) ==References== == External links == * * * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese female swimmers Category:Female freestyle swimmers Category:Asian Games medalists in swimming Category:Asian Games gold medalists for China Category:Swimmers at the 2014 Asian Games Category:Medalists at the 2014 Asian Games Category:Swimmers from Dalian
